        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Broken hearts seem not far away</l>
          <l>Wont you meet me there</l>
          <l>Cause I passed by you this morning</l>
          <l>But I cant pass you by</l>
          <l>Thinking of you in my mind </l>
          <l>Sunny day sunny day</l>
          <l>On a lonely aging way </l>
          <l>Broken hearts is a place where I</l>
          <l>Meet my sanity</l>
          <l>With a taste of a new beginning</l>
          <l>And leaving worlds behind</l>
          <l>Still youre always on my mind </l>
          <l>Sunny day sunny day</l>
          <l>On a lonely aging way </l>
          <l>Sunny day sunny day</l>
          <l>But my love is far away</l>
